  "detailed_description": "<h1>Wishlist Our Next Game</h1><p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Return home</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6001980eeec031e1da95bc810a5aba85.poster.avif?t=1700536721\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6001980eeec031e1da95bc810a5aba85.webm?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6001980eeec031e1da95bc810a5aba85.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You left the planet 200 years ago in search of a new life on the colonies, now you've returned against your will and must fight to survive in the post-apocalyptic world you once called home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight powerful enemies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/50d25d341738e514096bc481047756ae.poster.avif?t=1700536721\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/50d25d341738e514096bc481047756ae.webm?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/50d25d341738e514096bc481047756ae.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you explore the world, you'll encounter different enemies and bosses soaked with lore. Slaying them can reward you with new grimoire, relic era currency, parts for your ship, and mysterious treasures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore mysterious landscapes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/fcfd2f023e7d2ab52f84831a01979d35.poster.avif?t=1700536721\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/fcfd2f023e7d2ab52f84831a01979d35.webm?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/fcfd2f023e7d2ab52f84831a01979d35.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Your home has mutated and evolved since you've been gone. Explore the vast ruins of the city to the desolate valleys of the wasteland and uncover secrets of the past and present.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Meet new friends</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6c5c1b4d64fb64e6e389f19cd0f749cb.poster.avif?t=1700536721\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6c5c1b4d64fb64e6e389f19cd0f749cb.webm?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6c5c1b4d64fb64e6e389f19cd0f749cb.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>On your journey you'll make new friends who can reward your efforts of bravery and meet merchants who will sell you important items and weapons in exchange for the spoils of your adventure.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Upgrade your weapons</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/ae94a2cddd7395d1c4f3e319e9fa1f1f.poster.avif?t=1700536721\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/ae94a2cddd7395d1c4f3e319e9fa1f1f.webm?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/ae94a2cddd7395d1c4f3e319e9fa1f1f.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Purchase, unlock, and upgrade powerful new weapons to fight enemies. Keep your favorite weapons and upgrade them throughout the game with mastery points.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy now</h2>",
  "about_the_game": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Return home</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6001980eeec031e1da95bc810a5aba85.poster.avif?t=1700536721\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6001980eeec031e1da95bc810a5aba85.webm?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/6001980eeec031e1da95bc810a5aba85.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>You left the planet 200 years ago in search of a new life on the colonies, now you've returned against your will and must fight to survive in the post-apocalyptic world you once called home.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Fight powerful enemies</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/50d25d341738e514096bc481047756ae.poster.avif?t=1700536721\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/50d25d341738e514096bc481047756ae.webm?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/50d25d341738e514096bc481047756ae.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>As you explore the world, you'll encounter different enemies and bosses soaked with lore. Slaying them can reward you with new grimoire, relic era currency, parts for your ship, and mysterious treasures.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore mysterious landscapes</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/fcfd2f023e7d2ab52f84831