_item_assets/steam/apps/1537080/extras/ae94a2cddd7395d1c4f3e319e9fa1f1f.mp4?t=1700536721\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Purchase, unlock, and upgrade powerful new weapons to fight enemies. Keep your favorite weapons and upgrade them throughout the game with mastery points.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Buy now</h2>",
